description: Updates a Amazon Q Business application that is linked to a Amazon QuickSight account.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon QuickSight account that is connected to the Amazon Q Business application that you want to update.

parameters.name: ApplicationId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Q Business application that you want to update.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
